# Python (doc build pipeline)

The only application Python in this repo today is under `scripts/` (Mermaid pre-processing, Quarto/Pandoc rendering).

## Tooling

- **Python 3.14**
- **`ruff`** — lint and format (not black)
- **`uv`** — environments and packages

## Type hints (modern syntax)

- PEP 695 `type` aliases for aliases
- `X | Y` unions (not `Union[X, Y]`)
- Lowercase generics: `list[str]`, `dict[str, int]`
- `str | None` (not `Optional[str]`)

## Style

- Read a file before editing; match existing structure in `scripts/`.
- Validate paths; prefer explicit errors over silent failure.

Broader shell and repo conventions: **`AGENTS.md`**.
